## Prompt Template (Copy & Use)

```markdown
Create a comprehensive task summary with:

1. What was completed (bullet points with file changes)
2. What's in progress (with % complete)
3. What remains to be done (priority order)
4. Technical decisions made and why
5. Breaking changes (if any)
6. Specific next actions for next agent
7. Any blockers with suggested solutions
8. Test results

Use the detailed template from .agent/workflows/task-summary.md

Save to:
- .agent/state/task.md
- .agent/state/checkpoints/handover-[YOUR_PLATFORM]-[TIME].json
- project-log-md/[YOUR_PLATFORM]/session-summary-[TIME].md
- Update .agent/PROJECT_STATUS.md
```

